{"tid":1122806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[北極馬拉松2019] 香港馬拉松一哥 徐志堅奪得賽事冠軍 替香港人爭光","createTime":"2019-04-24T06:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T07:04:02.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12cc4394b96ba9eb2ddc34b219dafa54094e9735","tid":1122806,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%89%E6%9D%BE-2019-%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%90%E5%BF%97%E5%A0%85%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%258B%2589%25E6%259D%25BE-2019-%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25A0%2585%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0-2.jpg&h=d1f2c4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港華人馬拉松紀錄保持者徐志堅，於剛剛舉行的北極馬拉松賽 North Pole Marathon，以3小時01分43秒衝線，贏得賽事冠軍!<br />\n<br />\n賽後徐志堅「堅叔」憶述，比賽初段氣溫回升至攝氏2度，相對較為溫暖，他可以脫下外套著短袖衫作賽，跑得較為輕鬆。跑至第四圈 (全馬共要跑四圈)，氣溫驟降，他要穿回外套跑。但整體而言，全程要頂著大風，「堅叔」表示這是一場「我其中一場跑過最辛苦的馬拉松」!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%89%E6%9D%BE-2019-%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%90%E5%BF%97%E5%A0%85%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%258B%2589%25E6%259D%25BE-2019-%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25A0%2585%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0-4.jpg&h=179dcd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%89%E6%9D%BE-2019-%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%90%E5%BF%97%E5%A0%85%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%258B%2589%25E6%259D%25BE-2019-%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25A0%2585%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0-3.jpg&h=1d58c477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「堅叔」補充:「大部分我參加過的馬拉松都可以在３小時內完成，所以賽前的目標是希望能在3小時內完成賽事，最後多花了一分鐘左右算是一種小遺憾，但成績還算滿意。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然未能 sub-3 完賽，但「堅叔」這次能奪魁回歸，也能替香港人爭光!<br />\n<br />\n同場的香港藝人梁釗峰與劉心悠亦有好表現，各自以2小時15分51秒及3小時17分50秒完成半馬賽事，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%89%E6%9D%BE-2019-%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%90%E5%BF%97%E5%A0%85%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%258B%2589%25E6%259D%25BE-2019-%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25A0%2585%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0-5.jpg&h=db37cdf0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91b86e79facc5fe982b724ccb8e1c5e4f23ec456","tid":1122806,"uid":125978,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"哂呢d時間去跑馬拉松不如打多份工儲多個錢買車買樓啦，有錢收咩依家。<br />\n<br />\n你有車有樓理得你殺人放火都會有人尊重。"},{"pid":"ab14aa70860aa0e75192f68226285c8ea944533b","tid":1122806,"uid":1043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b86e79facc5fe982b724ccb8e1c5e4f23ec456","tid":1122806,"uid":125978,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"哂呢d時間去跑馬拉松不如打多份工儲多個錢買車買樓啦，有錢收咩依家。<br />\n<br />\n你有車有樓理得你殺人放火都會有人尊重。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"2008d81fd8764a563c3f242f68537e672abacb76","tid":1122806,"uid":73043